headline: Regency Centers Invites You to Join Its Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings Conference Call
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Jan. 06, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Regency Centers Corporation (“Regency Centers” or the “Company”) (NASDAQ: REG) will announce its fourth quarter 2024 earnings results on Thursday, February 6, 2025, after the market closes. The Company’s earnings release and supplemental information package will be posted on the Investor Relations section of the Company’s website – investors.regencycenters.com.
